						               													<description>Vamos ao quadro (Let&amp;rsquo;s go to the black board) is a game for two to four players acting as student.&amp;#10;The goal is to complete the challenges on the books to get exam cards. Each exam card provides the player with points. Whoever has the most points at the end of the game, wins.&amp;#10;Using dice, players can collect the tiles needed to form words, numbers, signs, among other things, to complete the challenges on the books.&amp;#10;In each turn, there are three actions for each student: one mandatory and two optional. Before starting, students should look at their books and see what pieces they will need.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     &amp;ldquo;Go to the board&amp;rdquo; - Allocate dice and perform the dice actions. (mandatory)&amp;#10;     &amp;ldquo;Group work&amp;rdquo; - Exchange tiles with another student. (optional)&amp;#10;     &amp;ldquo;Take a test&amp;rdquo; - Deliver all needed tiles to earn an exam card. (optional)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer (English)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;ldquo;Vamos ao quadro&amp;rdquo; &amp;eacute; um jogo para dois a quatro jogadores.&amp;#10;O objetivo &amp;eacute; completar os desafios dos livros para obter cartas de prova. Cada carta de prova atribui ao jogador pontos e quem tiver mais pontos ganha.&amp;#10;Atrav&amp;eacute;s dos dados, os jogadores conseguem recolher as fichas que necessitam para formar palavras, n&amp;uacute;meros, sinais, entre outras coisas, de forma a completar os desafios dos livros.&amp;#10;Em cada turno, existem tr&amp;ecirc;s a&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es para cada aluno, uma obrigat&amp;oacute;ria e duas opcionais. Antes de come&amp;ccedil;ar os alunos devem observar os seus livros e ver que fichas &amp;eacute; que ir&amp;atilde;o precisar. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;     &amp;ldquo;Ir ao quadro&amp;rdquo; - Alocar os dados e fazer a a&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o desses dados. (a&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o obrigat&amp;oacute;ria) &amp;#10;     &amp;ldquo;Trabalho de grupo&amp;rdquo; - Trocar fichas com outro aluno. (opcional) &amp;#10;     &amp;ldquo;Fazer uma prova&amp;rdquo; - Entregar todas as fichas necess&amp;aacute;rias para conquistar uma carta de disciplina. (opcional)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer (Portuguese)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
